e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T19:44:11.000Z","msg":"東壩唔洗禁區紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發現鳩噏柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179e5add2a0ad2c26dfcd776d5a7bc8f0776315c","tid":357111,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T20:02:15.000Z","msg":"冇車咪學人9up啦"},{"pid":"2aca65fe4737340c685d36cc3817a726e37e26f7","tid":357111,"uid":63734,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T20:08:02.000Z","msg":"撚有位泊<br />\n撚有禁區紙<br />\n睇完撚有精神揸返出市區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你條9up仔 隔住個mon話人窮想暗示自己好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8b0028e6ba3e1ba605c2ef48658afe30fc14ac","tid":357111,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T20:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我見康文署有段野咁寫, 即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n許 可 證 只 容 許 申 請 機 構 在 已預約 的 日 期 使 用 萬 宜 路<br />\n(下圖紅色所示路段 )<br />\n往 返 北 潭 涌 關 閘 及 天 文 公 園。如 發 現 車 輛 駛 入 下 圖 萬 宜 路 非 紅 色 部 分 或 禁 區 內 其 他 道 路 ， 即 作 違 規 論 ， 該 學 校 或 團 體 日 後 的 申 請 將 不 受 理 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o7bz6exu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo7bz6exu&h=f4292812&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該代表紅色路段唔洗禁區紙<br />\n利申1個月前去左東壩，都唔洗禁區紙</blockquote><br />\n呀唔係喎，睇段文字又好似真係要</blockquote><br />\n咪講得好清楚囉.<br />\n申請呢張《車輛經萬宜路至天文公園許可證》禁區紙. 只可以進入張圖紅色既路段. <br />\n如果你要入到去東霸,你係要申請第二張禁區紙<br />\n入到東霸, 如果係團體, 記憶中要向水務處申請, 再向漁農處申請, 每日好似只准5個團體定巴士入<br />\n<br />\n成班窮撚. 有錢緊係租隻遊艇去香港海域最東南邊睇啦.<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/water/marine_quality/images/mapc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwater%2Fmarine_quality%2Fimages%2Fmapc.jpg&h=09cfb267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"470485c104aa288d8693e810f002f07310e7c821","tid":357111,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T20:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬有禁區紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定要係萬宜水庫睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒到...<br />\n<br />\n渣車番屋企電視睇啦不如<br />\n<br />\n縮番入老母閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0facb4d040963f0917fadb08d707e22149b19cb8","tid":357111,"uid":35193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T20:35:07.000Z","msg":"大家唔好怪樓豬<br />\n其實樓豬就係車人上去果啲的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都算有車嘅"},{"pid":"eda268dd699c021c0b1d6bd1a432dd89c86d35f7","tid":357111,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩噏真係唔使成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就系有尼d會然 搞到禾地科林低汁左巧多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8b0274b14f8dc1c0488c85b3a0dfc55f29f9e1","tid":357111,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬有禁區紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定要係萬宜水庫睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好兜啦 好柒啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明你真係無車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇得流星都係半夜三更去郊區<br />\n有車嘅人點會專登去一個自己揸唔到車嘅郊區? 明明有好多地方都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然有車嘅人都會有時坐的士/地鐵<br />\n但而家唔係坐出旺角喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd92fa1fffe6d64ddc4ac371aab346725afd810","tid":357111,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我見康文署有段野咁寫, 即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n許 可 證 只 容 許 申 請 機 構 在 已預約 的 日 期 使 用 萬 宜 路<br />\n(下圖紅色所示路段 )<br />\n往 返 北 潭 涌 關 閘 及 天 文 公 園。如 發 現 車 輛 駛 入 下 圖 萬 宜 路 非 紅 色 部 分 或 禁 區 內 其 他 道 路 ， 即 作 違 規 論 ， 該 學 校 或 團 體 日 後 的 申 請 將 不 受 理 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o7bz6exu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo7bz6exu&h=f4292812&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該代表紅色路段唔洗禁區紙<br />\n利申1個月前去左東壩，都唔洗禁區紙</blockquote><br />\n呀唔係喎，睇段文字又好似真係要</blockquote><br />\n紅綫只係去到西壩<br />\n東壩冇show 出嚟"},{"pid":"1d3b713925e517ad144f12e87d92df442edf6cbf","tid":357111,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得呢d 無謂野既人都有錢架啦<br />\n😂<br />\n你幾時見窮撚會為左影張相post ig 呃like 咁落力</blockquote><br />\n咁係你眼中既「有錢人」其實都係窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d246153e7979b1263d6b2ded40b0759aae4546b","tid":357111,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇車咪學人9up啦</blockquote><br />\n我fb有車嘅朋友全都都係揸去其他地方睇<img src=\"/a